1. *Delo* koje je napisao pisac je postalo veoma popularno. (The *work* written by the author has become very popular.)
2. Ova fabrika *proizvodi* delove za automobile. (This factory *produces* parts for cars.)
3. *Deo* grada u kome živim je vrlo miran. (The *part* of the city where I live is very quiet.)
4. Da li si *delio* novac sa svojim prijateljima? (Did you *share* the money with your friends?)
5. Moramo da *razdelimo* zadatke i da ih što pre obavimo. (We need to *divide* the tasks and complete them as soon as possible.)
6. Ovaj film mi se *dopadao* zbog odlične glume i *zanimljive* priče. (I *liked* this movie because of the excellent acting and *interesting* story.)
7. Reči ovog pesnika me uvek *diraju* i *nadahnjuju*. (The words of this poet always *move* and *inspire* me.)
8. Tokom školske godine, profesor nam je dosta *delio* savete o učenju i uspehu. (During the school year, the teacher *shared* a lot of advice with us about learning and success.)
9. *Deluje* mi da će ova godina biti bolja od prethodne. (It *seems* to me that this year will be better than the previous one.)
10. Kada *delimo* hranu sa drugima, treba da mislimo i na one kojima je najpotrebnija. (When we *share* food with others, we should also think about those who need it the most.)